      <title>特朗普将在财政部长遴选过程中会见沃什和罗文</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-20/trump-to-meet-warsh-rowan-in-treasury-secretary-search-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普继续物色财政部长，他计划周三与前美联储理事凯文·沃什和阿波罗全球管理公司 (Apollo Global Management Inc.) 的马克·罗文 (Marc Rowan) 进行面谈。彭博电视台的安玛丽·霍登 (Annmarie Hordern) 报道了此事。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-20/trump-to-meet-warsh-rowan-in-treasury-secretary-search-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 13:20:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塔吉特因销售持平、库存增加下调利润预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-20/target-cuts-profit-outlook-on-inventory-flat-sales-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塔吉特下调了全年盈利预期，警告称本季度销售持平和库存增加损害了盈利能力。Gordon Haskett Research 零售业高级分析师查克·格罗姆 (Chuck Grom) 在“彭博监测”中分析了这一结果。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-20/target-cuts-profit-outlook-on-inventory-flat-sales-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 13:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着降级希望逐渐消退，B&M 成为今年表现最差的 FTSE 100 股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/b-m-is-worst-ftse-100-stock-this-year-as-trading-down-hopes-fade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[B&amp;M European Value Retail SA 股价连续第四天下跌，由于折扣店能在经济低迷时期抢占市场份额的希望逐渐消退，该股成为今年以来富时 100 指数中表现最差的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/b-m-is-worst-ftse-100-stock-this-year-as-trading-down-hopes-fade</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 13:01:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国锌业巨头争夺控制权 争夺战愈演愈烈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-20/korea-zinc-boss-fights-for-control-amid-takeover-battle-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国锌业公司首席执行官崔允彬告诉彭博社记者 Stephen Engle，在公司被迫放弃通过发行新股筹集 18 亿美元的计划后，他正在努力重新赢得股东的信任。这对崔允彬抵御最大股东 Young Poong 和私募股权公司 MBK Partners 恶意收购的努力造成了打击。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-20/korea-zinc-boss-fights-for-control-amid-takeover-battle-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 12:55:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
